						               													<description>Thousands of years ago, the Book of Eternity was placed on a bridge with four sacred guardians of white and black magic to defend the balance between the forces of good and evil.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The magic that emanates from the book has sparked an ambition among its guardians who now struggle to the death to reach it and be the holder of the power of the book.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Choose your side and help the guardians to take possession of the Miraculum, the Book of Eternity.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Miraculum is a quick game based on the throw of dice to be played in pairs (2x2) or in duel mode (1x1), where you will have to choose between defending white magic or black magic.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You and your opponents will fight to the death to be the new holder of the holy book, the Miraculum.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, you will have to combine the result of your dice to be able to cast spells to attack, protect, walk, push, trap, poison, heal, reverse position or even summon a werewolf against your enemies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are two ways to win the game:&amp;#10;- Killing all wizards of the opposite color by throwing them off the bridge; or&amp;#10;- Arriving and taking possession of the Book of Eternity, the Miraculum.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
